snippet.title: Pro Philosopher 2: Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Pro Philosopher 2 will release October 8th, 2024! To celebrate, we're revealing some of the most opinionated members of our cast... Karl Marx, and YOUR MOM.
WISHLIST NOW, or check out the DEMO: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2120070/Pro_Philosopher_2_Governments__Grievances/
